wbedtf-desc: Adde a Wikibase le supporto del standard EDTF per medio de un typo de datos dedicate
wikibase-listdatatypes-edtf-body:
Un data o hora in le formato [https://www.loc.gov/standards/datetime/ Extended Date/Time Format (EDTF)].

Iste formato es disponibile perque le [https://github.com/ProfessionalWiki/WikibaseEdtf extension Wikibase EDTF] es activate. Vide le [https://github.com/ProfessionalWiki/WikibaseEdtf#wikibase-edtf documentation] del extension pro plus information sur su uso.
